Cell.Data: CWE Standards Model Summary for C / C++
The LDRA tool suite® is developed and certified to BS EN ISO 9001:2000.
This information is applicable to version 9.4.4 of the LDRA tool suite®. It is correct as of 25th April 2014.

Compliance is measured against "Common Weakness Enumeration. A Community-Developed Dictionary of Software Weakness Types. Version 2.4" 2013 Copyright © The MITRE Corporation
Further information is available at http://cwe.mitre.org
